UN Is Looking to Encourage Energy-Efficiency Projects in the Carbon Market

-- B y   E w a   K r u k o w s k a
-- 
2011-04-14T11:46:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/un-is-looking-to-encourage-energy-efficiency-projects-in-the-carbon-market.html
The regulators of the  United
Nations ’ Clean Development Mechanism are seeking to increase the
number of projects to boost  energy efficiency  in the carbon-
reduction program, UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
Executive Secretary Christiana Figueres said.  Figueres told a conference in Brussels today that she’s
pleased to see the private sector increasingly looking to raise
energy efficiencies. While the UN agreement in Cancun last
December was an important step forward, there remains an urgent
need to reduce emissions, she said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ewa Krukowska in Brussels at 
 ekrukowska@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Randall Hackley at 
 rhackley@bloomberg.net  